title: Lords of War T1 - T2 (2012) (Sosich&V2) cbr
description:
KALI is small second-class private military company that emerged in Serbia on the ruins of the last European war in 2019. The hired mercenaries are poorly paid and don't have a big life expectancy, but the company has its advantages. Among which are liberal and not very particular ways of recruitment.
This allows Stephane Marik, a man with troubled past, to quickly become a Meka driver.
The war in the Balkans was the first training ground for these modern tanks.

enjoy
